reviewText: love it,  great sale, great store.
Received this tape in better condition than stated. Was fast geting here also. Would recommened this store to all.

My 6 yr. old twin grandsons really like the Bananas Pajamas videos.  "Wish Fairies" is cute and keeps them entertained.  They watch this video over and over.  It is nice to have a wholesome video for them to watch.
